        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_1                                         = 10059,  -- What song do you want to hear? (1) Next Page. Field Battle (Solo). Field Battle (Party). Dungeon Battle (Solo). Dungeon Battle (Party). Windurst. San d'Oria. Bastok. Chateau d'Oraguille. Metalworks. Heavens Tower. Jeuno. Ru'Lude Gardens. Selbina. Mahura. Ronfaure. Sarutabaruta. Gustaberg. Batallia Downs. Sauromugue Champaign. Rolanberry Fields.
        WHAT_SONG_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_2                                         = 10060,  -- What song do you want to hear? (2) Next Page. Northlands. Delkfutt's Tower. Castle Zvahl. Shadow Lord Battle. Shadow Lord Theme. Bravery. Ghelsba. Ferry. Prelude. Mog House. Installation. Game Over, man! Airship. No Hope 1. No Hope 2. Anger. Sadness. Mid-Boss. Sometime, Somewhere. Memories. Uneasy. Theme (2). Theme (3).
