        FOR_YOUR_OWN_SAFETY_IT_IS_RECOMMENDED_THAT                              = 10064,  -- For your own safety, it is recommended that you set this location as your home point after changing jobs.
        HUH_NEVER_HEARD_THAT_NAME_BEFORE_IS_THAT                                = 10065,  -- Huh? %? Never heard that name before. Is that somebody famous? Oh, that's you?
        HMM_I_M_GUESSING_YOU_HAVEN_T_BEEN                                       = 10066,  -- Hmm. I'm guessing you haven't been taking on many requests from people. You know, if you keep that up, no one is going to remember you.
        EVEN_DOING_SMALL_FAVORS_IS_FINE_AT_FIRST                                = 10067,  -- Even doing small favors is fine at first. If you help out a lot of different people, you'll slowly gain their trust. Before you know it, everyone will know your name.
        I_THINK_I_HAVE_SOME_VAGUE_MEMORY_OF                                     = 10068,  -- ...%? I think I have some vague memory of hearing that name somewhere... Nope, it's gone.
        BUT_THIS_JUST_GOES_TO_SHOW_HOW_FEW                                      = 10069,  -- But this just goes to show how few people know you around here. You've gotta put yourself out there more, my young adventurer friend.
        HM_I_VE_HEARD_THAT_NAME_BEFORE_SEEMS                                    = 10070,  -- Hm? %? I've heard that name before. Seems you're building yourself a good reputation.
        BUT_YOU_VE_STILL_GOT_A_LONG_WAY                                         = 10071,  -- But you've still got a long way to go until you can say you're truly famous. The journey of a thousand miles starts with a single step, so keep at it!
        HELLO_I_VE_HEARD_YOUR_NAME_MENTIONED_ONCE                               = 10072,  -- Hello, %. I've heard your name mentioned once or twice around these parts lately.
        YOU_RE_COMING_UP_IN_THE_WORLD_BUT                                       = 10073,  -- You're coming up in the world, but don't slow down now!
        OH_IT_S_YOUR_NAME_COMES_UP_QUITE                                        = 10074,  -- Oh, it's %. Your name comes up quite a lot in conversation these days. You must be keeping busy out there.
        LISTENING_TO_THE_TALK_ABOUT_YOU_AROUND_THE                              = 10075,  -- Listening to the talk about you around the oasis just makes me swell up with pride. I know it's strange, but I love to hear about adventurers doing well in Rabao. Keep up the good work, %.
        WOW_THERE_S_HARDLY_A_SOUL_IN_ALL                                        = 10076,  -- Wow, %! There's hardly a soul in all of Rabao who hasn't heard your name! I could hardly believe the stir you've been making.
        YOU_VE_ENTERED_THE_RANKS_OF_THE_TRULY                                   = 10077,  -- You've entered the ranks of the truly great adventurers! But don't be content with your position; aim for the very top!
        EVERY_TIME_I_SPEAK_WITH_YOU_YOU_SEEM                                    = 10078,  -- %! Every time I speak with you, you seem to have gained in status. Pretty soon, I'm gonna have to start making appointments to talk to you!
        THERE_ISN_T_A_PERSON_IN_THE_WHOLE                                       = 10079,  -- There isn't a person in the whole of Rabao who hasn't heard of you. I never dreamed you would come so far!
        GREETINGS_YOUR_ENDEAVORS_IN_NEIGHBORING_COUNTRIES_HAVE_REACHED          = 10080,  -- Greetings, %. Your endeavors in neighboring countries have reached us here in Rabao, and the glory of your reputation precedes you.
        I_FEEL_HONORED_TO_HAVE_KNOWN_YOU_BEFORE                                 = 10081,  -- I feel honored to have known you before you became so famous. Good luck with your continuing adventurers!
        AH_I_VE_KNOWN_YOU_SINCE_YOU_WERE                                        = 10082,  -- Ah, %. I've known you since you were just starting out around here, but to think you would go on to achieve such glory...
        IN_RABAO_AND_BEYOND_YOUR_NAME_IS_ON                                     = 10083,  -- In Rabao and beyond, your name is on everyone's lips. It wouldn't be going too far to say you've achieved the status of hero in my eyes.
        MAY_THE_BLESSINGS_OF_THE_GODDESS_ALTANA_WATCH                           = 10084,  -- May the blessings of the Goddess Altana watch over your continuing endeavors.
