        WITHOUT_IT_YOU_WON_T_BE_GETTING_INSIDE                                  = 10103,  -- Without it, you won't be getting inside no matter how sneaky-weaky you are! Oh, and if you want to take some friends with you, they also have to get % from me. Okey-dokey?
