        DO_YOU_SEE_WHAT_I_HAVE_TO_DEAL                                          = 10165,  -- Do you see what I have to deal with? I don't know how much longer I can work with such a pessimist.
        THAT_S_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN_I_WAS                                          = 10166,  -- That's where you come in. I was thinking of letting one of you adventurers test out the new fork and prove to my colleague that it is able to return data valuable to his research.
