        ARE_YOU_SURE_YOU_ARE_READY_OFF_TO                                       = 10181,  -- Are you sure you are ready? Off to [Ifrit's Cauldron/the Quicksand Caves/the Den of Rancor/Cape Teriggan/Fei'Yin/the Boyahda Tree]! My dog ate my mini tuning fork. Not just yet...
