        IF_YOU_DO_NOT_BRING_THE_WE_GAVE                                         = 10186,  -- If you do not bring the % we gave you, my companion cannot warp you to [Ifrit's Cauldron/the Quicksand Caves/the Den of Rancor/Cape Teriggan/Fei'Yin/the Boyahda Tree].
        DID_YOU_REMEMBER_TO_BRING_THE                                           = 10187,  -- Did you remember to bring the %?
