        CHELVADURAI_WE_WERE_JUST_TALKING_ABOUT_YOU_THE                          = 10540,  -- Chelvadurai, we were just talking about you. The adventurer we hired has returned. Now, about Sanctia...
        SHE_S_BECOME_AN_ADVENTURER_AND_THIS_PACKAGE                             = 10541,  -- She's become an adventurer! And this package is for me...?
        THERE_S_A_LETTER_INSIDE_SANCTIA_SAYS_THAT                               = 10542,  -- There's a letter inside. Sanctia says that she'll send more money from her adventures so that I can pay back my loans and go back to my wife...
        SHE_S_A_GOOD_KID_TIME_FOR_YOU                                           = 10543,  -- She's a good kid. Time for you to pull up your bootstraps and follow her example.
        I_INTEND_TO_DO_JUST_THAT_MISTER_ZORIBOH                                 = 10544,  -- I intend to do just that, Mister Zoriboh.
        THANKS_FOR_ALL_YOUR_HELP_IT_S_NOT                                       = 10545,  -- Thanks for all your help, %. It's not much, but here's a little something from me.
        IF_YOU_RUN_INTO_LITTLE_SANCTIA_AGAIN_ON                                 = 10546,  -- If you run into little Sanctia again on your travels, make sure she's keeping out of mischief.
        I_LL_NEVER_LET_HER_DOWN_AGAIN_IF                                        = 10547,  -- I'll never let her down again. If Sanctia grows weary of her new life, you tell her she always has a place here with me.
        SANCTIA_S_STILL_YOUNG_AND_FULL_OF_FIRE                                  = 10548,  -- Sanctia's still young and full of fire. I'm sure she'll make a fine adventurer.
        I_HEARD_THE_NEWS_FROM_CHELVADURAI_WHO_D                                 = 10549,  -- I heard the news from Chelvadurai. Who'd have thought that girl would get her head out of the clouds long enough to do something constructive?
        WELL_AS_LONG_AS_I_GET_MY_MONEY                                          = 10550,  -- Well, as long as I get my money back, I'm not really concerned either way. I've heard adventurers can make a fortune these days...
