        AH_ANOTHER_DEDICATED_SYNERGIST_LOOKING_TO_REFINE_HIS                    = 10606,  -- Ah, another dedicated synergist looking to refine his/her] technique. Excellent! That motivation will serve you well.
        BUT_I_M_AFRAID_YOU_LL_NEED_EXPERIENCE                                   = 10607,  -- ...But I'm afraid you'll need [/ever so slightly more/a bit more/more/a good deal more/considerably more] experience before you're ready to benefit from my training.
        AND_YES_IT_WOULD_SEEM_YOU_RE_AT                                         = 10608,  -- And yes, it would seem you're at just the right skill level to receive my training. So, what will it be? Which technique would you like to improve?
