        BY_INFUSING_ONE_S_BODY_WITH_ATMACITE_IT                                 = 10879,  -- By infusing one's body with atmacite, it is possible to obtain powers akin to those once possessed by the creature whence it came, rather like turning a beast's fangs upon its own kind.
        AT_FIRST_GLANCE_ATMACITE_APPEARS_TO_BE_THE                              = 10880,  -- At first glance, atmacite appears to be the perfect artificial enhancement. However, it does suffer from a single limitation: its power is unleashed only when engaged in a Voidwatch operation.
