        CRUOR_IS_OBTAINABLE_BY_VARIOUS_MEANS_FELLING_A                          = 10886,  -- Cruor is obtainable by various means, felling a Voidwalker being the most common of all. As you can never have too much cruor, I urge you to be diligent in its procurement.
        WE_VE_RECENTLY_PERFECTED_A_METHOD_FOR_IMPROVING                         = 10887,  -- We've recently perfected a method for improving atmacite potency. The process is called enrichment, and involves fusing cruor on to atmacite to amplify its power.
