        UNDER_NORMAL_CONDITIONS_ATMACITE_ENRICHMENT_IS_AN_INTENSIVE             = 10889,  -- Under normal conditions, atmacite enrichment is an intensive process that demands trained hands. For reasons yet to be determined, however, both infusion and enrichment can be safely performed by laymen, provided they're at a planar rift.
